1 Machine-Type Tuner + 1 or more non-Tuner "Superheavy Samurai" monstersThis card can attack while in Defense Position. If it does, apply its DEF for damage calculation. When this card is Synchro Summoned while you have no Spell/Trap Cards in your Graveyard: You can destroy all Spell/Trap Cards your opponent controls.
